              >Bootloader</strong
            > applications and <strong>I2C device drivers</strong> in <strong
              >C</strong
            > for the <strong>Symbol Generator (SG)</strong> and <strong
              >Rudder Assistant System (RAS)</strong
            > hardware. For the Avionics Modernization of Military Transport Aircraft,
            engineered an <strong>ARINC 429</strong> data simulator tool in <strong
              >C# (.NET Framework)</strong
            > to streamline <strong>verification environments</strong>.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
            <span
