            >
              <span>Avionics Architecture</span>
              <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-black opacity-30">02</span>
            </li>
            <li
              class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium border-b border-on-surface/5 pb-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
            >
